These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-1::.
House: futuristic, gothic-revival, craftsman
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, filmmaking, drawing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, indie, trance
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rabbit, turtle
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, project-manager, mechanic
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, aconite
 1. the person who growsaconite is the fan of indie##1
 2. the mechanic is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 3. the fan of gospel is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 4. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of indie is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 6. the person who growslily is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is the craftsman house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in the middle##1
 9. the futuristic house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
10. the photographer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |    3     |
| House      | futuristic | craftsman        | gothic-revival |
| Hobby          | drawing    | filmmaking        | photography    |
| Music-Genre   | trance        | gospel        | indie    |
| Pet           | turtle        | chinchilla    | rabbit   |
| Job         | project-manager    | mechanic | photographer |
| Flower     | daisy     | lily          | aconite     |

