City: venice, boston, colone
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, zombie
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, balloon-flower, begonia
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, handball, rugby
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, vegafina, bluemaster
1. the person traveling to venice is the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes grey is the vegafina-smoker##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
8. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who likes black##1
9. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |         3          |
| Color         | black    | grey     | pink            |
| City           | boston | venice | colone |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | satire      | zombie             |
| Flower   | marigold | begonia     | balloon-flower             |
| Sport         | handball  | rugby       | baseball           |
