6. the person eating zucchini is the ritmeester-smoker##1
7. the person eating lettuce is the person who's birthday is in april##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
9. the townhouse house is the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3       |
| Hobby         | video-games  | cooking     | skydiving    |
