The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, fishing, reading
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, snooker
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, helicopter, airplane
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, blend, oliveros
3 different pets are kept: goat, rabbit, rat
 1. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 4. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
 5. the blend-smoker is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 6. the person playing snooker is the person driving the airplane##1
 7. the owner of the rat is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
10. the blend-smoker is the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |
| Color          | mauve | fuchsia | purple        |
| Hobby         | fishing  | dancing   | reading     |
| Game           | snooker  | mah-jongg | canasta |
| Transport   | airplane  | car   | helicopter     |
| Cigar   | blend  | siglo  | oliveros      |
| Pet           | rabbit   | rat       | goat        |

