 7. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the mechanic##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 9. the chef is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | coffee    | milk     | water         |
| Game          | monopoly  | poker    | backgammon         |
| Job           | fisherman | mechanic | chef          |
| Birthday   | may    | october      | july        |
| Pet   | hedgehog     | chinchilla     | goat          |
| Cigar         | pall-mall    | dannemann | swisher |

