.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-20::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, chess
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, filmmaking, hiking
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, coffee
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, nigerian, russian
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, lily, sunflower
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, march, december
1. the person drinking sprite is in the middle##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the chinese is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the person who growssunflower is in the middle##1
7. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who growslily##1
8. the chinese is on the far left##1
9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3       |
| Game          | monopoly          | chess      | scrabble      |
| Hobby         | hiking        | filmmaking | dancing      |
| Beverage   | juice          | sprite        | coffee       |
| Nationality   | chinese       | nigerian   | russian      |
| Flower           | lily           | sunflower      | bellflower         |
| Birthday         | december | january    | march |

 